data.description: Welcome to this San Antonio masterpiece, where luxury meets functionality with plenty of extras to make this home truly a one of a kind. This exquisite 5 bedroom 3.5 bath boasts an impressive 2622 sqft open floorplan, exuding elegance and comfort in every corner.   Designed for entertainment and relaxation, this home features multiple living and dining areas, each offering a unique ambiance. The kitchen is a culinary paradise, featuring state-of-the-art Frigidaire stainless steel appliances: gas range, refrigerator, microwave, dishwasher, and a Hydronix Reverse Osmosis Water System. The kitchen boasts plentiful granite counterspace, accented by a chic tile backsplash, with rich espresso wooden cabinetry. Tranquility is found in the expansive primary suite and private spa-like bathroom, featuring a double vanity, expansive walk-in closet, serene garden tub, and a separate stand-up shower. Upstairs, the Texas-sized game room / media room presents an ideal space for lounging and entertainment. Four additional bedrooms are also found upstairs each offering a generous size and closet space, ensuring comfort for all. The 2-car garage, is a treasure trove of extras featuring a GE Pro Elite Soft Water Filtration System, dual Gas Water Heaters and a durable epoxy flooring. The home has also been upgraded with a Hunter Sprinkler system and an in-wall pest control system, showcasing the home's meticulous attention to detail. The backyard is a canvas for your imagination, offering ample space for a pool or whatever your heart desires, complete with a shed and a large covered patio. The presence of a vibrant orange tree in the garden infuses a natural charm. This home is priced to sell fast so schedule your tour today!
